              <span class="tag effort">Effort: Low</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-section">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="card faq-card">
        <h3>What is a good first date idea?</h3>
        <p>A good first date is usually low-pressure and allows for conversation. Coffee dates, a walk in the park, or visiting a museum are excellent choices.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card faq-card">
        <h3>How much should I spend on a date?</h3>
        <p>There is no set amount. It depends entirely on your budget and what you are comfortable with. Many fantastic dates are completely free.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card faq-card">
        <h3>What are some good dates for introverts?</h3>
        <p>Introverts often prefer quieter environments. Bookstore dates, movie nights at home, or a quiet dinner at a low-key restaurant are great options.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card faq-card">
        <h3>How do I plan a surprise date?</h3>
        <p>Consider your partner's interests and schedule. Plan the logistics in advance, and tell them what to wear without revealing the destination.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card faq-card">
        <h3>What are good winter date ideas?</h3>
        <p>Ice skating, indoor rock climbing, visiting a hot springs, or an elaborate indoor fort building session make for great winter dates.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card faq-card">
        <h3>How to choose the right date idea?</h3>
        <p>Think about what both you and your partner enjoy. A mix of comfort and trying something slightly new is usually a safe bet.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card faq-card">
        <h3>What are some good double date ideas?</h3>
        <p>Escape rooms, trivia nights, bowling, or hosting a dinner party are excellent activities that work well for groups of four.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script is:inline>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      const categoryFilter = document.getElementById('category-filter');
      const budgetFilter = document.getElementById('budget-filter');
      const randomizerBtn = document.getElementById('randomizer-btn');
      const categorySections = document.querySelectorAll('.category-section');
      const ideaCards = document.querySelectorAll('.idea-card');

      function applyFilters() {
        const catValue = categoryFilter.value;
        const budValue = budgetFilter.value;

        categorySections.forEach(section => {
          const matchesCat = catValue === 'all' || section.dataset.category === catValue;
          let hasVisibleCards = false;

          const cards = section.querySelectorAll('.idea-card');
          cards.forEach(card => {
            card.classList.remove('highlight');
            const matchesBud = budValue === 'all' || card.dataset.budget === budValue;
            if (matchesCat && matchesBud) {
              card.style.display = 'block';
              hasVisibleCards = true;
            } else {
              card.style.display = 'none';
            }
          });

          section.style.display = hasVisibleCards ? 'block' : 'none';
        });
      }

      function pickRandom() {
        categoryFilter.value = 'all';
        budgetFilter.value = 'all';
        applyFilters();

        const visibleCards = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.idea-card[style="display: block;"]'));
        if (visibleCards.length === 0) return;

        const randomCard = visibleCards[Math.floor(Math.random() * visibleCards.length)];
        ideaCards.forEach(c => c.classList.remove('highlight'));
        randomCard.classList.add('highlight');
        randomCard.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });
      }

      categoryFilter.addEventListener('change', applyFilters);
      budgetFilter.addEventListener('change', applyFilters);
      randomizerBtn.addEventListener('click', pickRandom);

      applyFilters();
    });
  </script>

